OL,5, Author Salman Rushdie has begun his    
OL,6, "road to recovery" but it will be long,
OL,7, his agent says.                        
OL,9,FMr Rushdie, 75, was left severely      
OL,10,Finjured after being stabbed on stage   
OL,11,Fwhile speaking at an event in New York 
OL,12,Fstate.                                 
OL,14,FHe has faced years of death threats for
OL,15,Fhis novel The Satanic Verses, which    
OL,16,Fsome Muslims see as blasphemous.       
OL,18,FThe man charged over Friday's attack   
OL,19,Fhas pleaded not guilty to attempted    
OL,20,Fmurder.                                
